// Dragnet [Container]: dragnet-container-2026-2747 — Vulnerable Base Image Pull
// Status: deprecated | Level: high | ID: 278132b7-b6eb-5f45-9412-46d7d5ab53f3

#event_simpleName=*
| (ImageFileName = *debian:11* OR ImageFileName = *debian:12* OR ImageFileName = *debian:13* OR ImageFileName = *debian:14*)
| table([timestamp, ComputerName])
| limit(1000)
